{"tid":1083112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【麻疹肆虐】工會多次爭取 國泰終允機組人員戴口罩執勤","createTime":"2019-03-29T11:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T13:14:38.000Z","uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de69e454ee55328a82c134fccd0463514c92e1e4","tid":1083112,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/575000/577180/31WDDA2_ET0154402015033012233121_630_opt_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F575000%2F577180%2F31WDDA2_ET0154402015033012233121_630_opt_1024.jpg&h=735e1e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港麻疹疫情爆發，更在機場擴散，多名航空業從業員「中招」。國泰空服員梁小姐向本報投訴，指近日曾致電公司查詢，能否在航班當值期間佩戴口罩，卻獲對方告知不能佩戴口罩，對情況感憂慮，「想去打疫苗又冇機會打，喺航班當值又唔畀戴口罩，變咗保護唔到自己，真係好無奈，希望公司可以畀個最基本嘅保障。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20131117/large/17la6p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20131117%2Flarge%2F17la6p1.jpg&h=90f6f39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰空中服務員工會主席胡綺薇表示，今日再度去信管理層，嚴正要求在非常時期容許機組人員工作時可選擇戴口罩，尤其飛往疫情爆發的國家如日本、菲律賓及美國等。她表示麻疹疫情爆發初期，已先後發短訊和去信國泰管理層，要求加強與衞生署和機管局聯繫，優先讓機場員工和機組人員接種疫苗，並容許機組人員佩戴口罩，惟公司置若罔聞。她稱連日來收到很多空服員控訴，不滿公司罔顧員工安全，工會今日再度去信管理層提出嚴正要求●國泰今午回覆工會，終肯放寬規定，在過渡期內，容許未有麻疹免疫力的機組人員，執勤時戴口罩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170809/large/09la2p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170809%2Flarge%2F09la2p6.jpg&h=78c77e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n胡綺薇指雖然現行政策沒列明在機上執勤時不准戴口罩，但一直是不成文規定；除非機組人員在航班上突然感不適，否則一般情況下，機艙服務經理均不允許戴口罩，理由是為免引起乘客恐慌。但她認為，在麻疹疫情爆發下，國泰更應特事特辦，放寬有關規定，不能罔顧員工和乘客的安全，「乘客有需要時都會戴口罩，喺呢個非常時期，我哋工作時都戴上口罩，其實對雙方都有保障」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/vp/3c37306cbd76b4250f8443c856286036/5CB23620/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/s640x640/28429200_383287082138072_4356675114071228416_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F3c37306cbd76b4250f8443c856286036%2F5CB23620%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fs640x640%2F28429200_383287082138072_4356675114071228416_n.jpg&h=07a256de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰今午發出內部通告，指因應衞生防護中心的建議，當員工等待麻疹免疫力測試結果期間，公司會容許未有免疫力的員工在執勤時可考慮戴口罩，並需屬標準的外科手術口罩，且由員工自行負責，公司不會提供。國泰發言人指，國泰會遵照衞生署建議，於香港機場工作的同事及機組人員，應在出門上班前量度體溫。未注射麻疹疫苗的員工，可考慮於室內或機艙內工作時戴口罩，亦鼓勵同事核實是否已注射麻疹疫苗。若員工身體不適，公司亦建議立即就醫及留在家中休息。"},{"pid":"5fd258aba8fae78817216d11344e89b1f45b73eb","tid":1083112,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fd4fc11b6c86621d323a4bb47479539c940afa","tid":1083112,"uid":138916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e43a09080fac746f9649723b4e8fe09106cf33","tid":1083112,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"開頭做乜唔俾人戴口罩？"},{"pid":"86957b9efcba514432cc3563d62c9eadb6ea5100","tid":1083112,"uid":2536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e43a09080fac746f9649723b4e8fe09106cf33","tid":1083112,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"開頭做乜唔俾人戴口罩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"除非機組人員在航班上突然感不適，否則一般情況下，機艙服務經理均不允許戴口罩，理由是為免引起乘客恐慌。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e65a7802fe290116b472e504992cd900f408506","tid":1083112,"uid":78791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f07b43b2be527a15f3e406288c1fa84ffc206a8b","tid":1083112,"uid":50935,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0e65a7802fe290116b472e504992cd900f408506","tid":1083112,"uid":78791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩會靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ec4dabbb6be9c936b8168a38870377d49941a3","tid":1083112,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"on9港女用手指罅隔汽車廢氣<br />\n用外科口罩隔麻疹病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dcbb4a396cbbc50d067c992dea45035e6aa0dc","tid":1083112,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07b43b2be527a15f3e406288c1fa84ffc206a8b","tid":1083112,"uid":50935,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0e65a7802fe290116b472e504992cd900f408506","tid":1083112