y airborne spread when an infected person breathes, coughs, or sneezes. Measles virus can remain infectious in the air for up to two hours after an infected person leaves an area.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32029a64aa489bd183c4ba0445ba3a5e457a47a9","tid":1083112,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23eb87de62b08b0e7234d0603178572c6753a816","tid":1083112,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ccb92f2371353ced8b24a6ea6203b1a9c17aac7","tid":1083112,"uid":119145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 麻疹要n95先防到囉好冇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"麻疹是如何傳播的？<br />\n<br />\n麻疹可透過空氣中的飛沫或直接接觸患者的鼻喉分泌物而傳播，透過被鼻喉分泌物弄污的物件傳播的機會則較低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"連登對傳染病知識原來係咁缺乏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}